Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扮家家酒的遊戲  就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三千院凪不到拉斯維加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就無法得到黑椿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把她帶到那裡去就是你的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  這神神怪怪的法術…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算怎樣啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白櫻！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇小姐！雛菊小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顯然不是沒事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是救人的話能不能用點更好的救人方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊  這到底算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您精神一如既往比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  剛才的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說80%是鳥人的那位究竟是幹什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用那種胡來的救人方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不如就這樣被拐走了算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  綾崎颯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我被拐走了  姐姐會擔心我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想她會非常擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  一個人回去很危險的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒關係的  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,颯先生  那孩子到底是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是鶇琉璃  是…凪大小姐的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是個好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼說謊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明知道黑椿在拉斯維加斯警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果襲擊警察局很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就只能拐走三千院凪  強迫她去拿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,志藤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯獨不原諒你讓姐姐陷入危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  所以你是要背叛你的母親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不會背叛母親的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到和平解決這個問題的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你閉上嘴好好看著就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為交換…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,借我機票錢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…要多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,10萬日元左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太貴了！5萬就足夠了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,8萬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…5萬5！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,7萬！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可得找便宜的航空公司去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是為了這個來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西澤同學她們…今天真的去紐約了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她們到了紐約後似乎會考慮搭便車什麼的去拉斯維加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻笨蛋倉鼠一定以為紐約和拉斯維加斯之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就只有東京和橫濱之間的距離而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論哪個人都藉著放假去旅行或者去看演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不知道悠閒地休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙是所謂的現充嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…大小姐因為沒有人陪而感到寂寞了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰…誰會寂寞啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說後悔當初拒絕去看琉加小姐的演唱會之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才沒這回事呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒關係  就算沒有人陪您  我還是一直在您身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這算什麼安慰方式！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的  就在你身邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  就算小颯不在也無所謂  我還有鶇呢  還有鶇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇小姐的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被綁架了  剛剛有恐嚇信送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐嚇信？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎  瑪莉亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  內容非常可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}鶇琉璃在我們這裡\N想讓她活命的話\N就來拉斯維加斯吧\N要拿黑椿和鶇交換哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這字跡不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明顯是鶇小姐的字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道她利用被綁架作為藉口…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做出自導自演的綁架…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  鶇小姐是怎麼到拉斯維加斯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是真的被綁架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從這封信上看  應該是沒有那個可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去鶇住的公寓看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒有人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個笨蛋  真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她唯獨行動力很強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是拉斯維加斯也一定能有辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得我看了這封信  真的會飛去拉斯維加斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  她真是個徹徹底底的大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這壓倒性的靈光一閃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:40.59,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（賭博默示錄經典開司臉）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候  鶇放電了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…她一定是這樣想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要做到這一步？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自導自演的綁架  多奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼糾結於黑椿？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:08:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣就有去拉斯維加斯和大家見面的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  沒什麼深層含義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這本漫畫是鶇小姐覺得最有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她相信大小姐最終一定會去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這貌似是鶇小姐最中意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我明明都說過爸爸的遺物就是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過算了  那麼想要垃圾的話就送給她好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去拉斯維加斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:51.48,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「そこで　微笑ってて　くれないか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:10.66,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小さい頃　星の数ほど夢を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:19.29,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私が望めばなんでも　手に入ると思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:25.18,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}でも欲しいものは　全部　高い所にあって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}背伸びをしても届かないから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.27,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}見上げるのをやめた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:38.39,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だけど　あの日　君に出逢った…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:44.71,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}微笑みがくれた　生まれてきたその意味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.43,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}知ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:54.66,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたがこの世界にいると
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.71,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思うだけで　生きていける
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.09,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばした　その手つかむよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:08.08,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何度くじけたって　構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:11.55,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乗り越えるよ　だから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:16.20,OPJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「そこで　微笑ってて　くれないか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:51.48,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「你能不能在那裡為我而微笑呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:10.66,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小時候的夢想多如繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:19.29,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}本以為只要追尋便能到手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:25.18,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是想要的東西都在高處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:29.62,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使踮起腳尖也無法觸及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.27,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以我放棄了抬頭仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:38.39,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是那一天　我遇到了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:44.71,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你那燦爛的笑容教會了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.43,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生命的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:54.66,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你存在於這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.71,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我只要想到這點就能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.09,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我抓住你伸出的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:08.08,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無論遭遇幾度挫折　都毫不氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:11.55,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因為我們一定能渡過難關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:16.20,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「你能不能在那裡為我而微笑呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…黑椿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:02.75,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（原型為寶璣Marie-Antoinette Grande Complication N°1160 \N瑪麗皇后懷錶，價值3000萬美金，原版在1983年曾經失竊過）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑椿果真是懷錶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前聽說過一把同名的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是拿著這個的話  會招來很強的惡運的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…根據帝老爺所說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它能把得到它的人的好運全部趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是招來惡運的受到詛咒的懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而當兩支針交匯在數字8的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會得到不可思議的好運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上我認為這不是什麼好東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  瑪莉亞  作為嘗試  你先把它拿起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎——？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  在這種地方也不會發生什麼事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…雖然你說的也對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就放輕鬆地拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說有什麼感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這就是普通的懷錶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是運氣都被吹走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛…剛剛那是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我可什麼都不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,The void being airtight, so we need to ventilate it. Here accurately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎剛才是換氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛那麼巧是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,So... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣  快給我停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯給我臉向那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這果然是因為那懷錶的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然讓大小姐你們拿在手上是太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}裙子都要轉起圈來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與綁架犯談判之前就由我拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  不過談判在晚上九點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很長一段時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經習慣惡運纏身了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  保證大小姐的安全不正是我這管家的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧  黑椿就拜託你了  小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  放心交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉亞  把黑椿給小颯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼又來啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕走好運  招來惡運…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是被詛咒的懷錶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會有人希望得到這東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過難得來到拉斯維加斯  有什麼有趣的事情可做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  米科諾斯島之後就沒跟小颯出過國了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…應該要創造一點開心的回憶才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我們乾脆去一下51區吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:10.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（51區：位於美國內華達州南部林肯郡，有空軍基地駐紮，被認為是\N美國用來秘密開發測試新的空軍飛行器的的地方，也有很多UFO的傳言）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  這是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就這樣定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉亞  快準備好車子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算它是招來惡運的懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來也沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真危險啊  差一點就被撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說大小姐的父親就是因為交通事故去世的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我得小心才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…咦  大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  馬上就迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  這怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先給瑪莉亞小姐打個電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（你的人生  就算充電也沒戲啦）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂——！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛還是滿電量的  怎麼突然間就沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成是故障了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子我都沒辦法跟其他人聯繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這下子麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉亞小姐  大小姐  你們在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  瑪莉亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  瑪莉亞  小颯人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  剛剛還在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  小颯他一下子就迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看…看來是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  給他打個電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您拔打的電話處於電波無法到達的地區或已經關掉電源無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無法接通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  迷路的話問一下路不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這多簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯…不會說英語吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  錢！他身上有錢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  小颯大危機啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去救他吧  瑪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？到哪裡去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  不好了  完全迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這可麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西澤同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  這不是西澤同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這問題應該我問你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯怎麼會在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  我們是因為有緊急的事情才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  我也知道西澤同學來了美國
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不是到紐約去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在約一小時之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為機體故障  飛機在拉斯維加斯降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一小時之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我拿到黑椿的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這懷錶是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  呃…這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  是我想太多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  就是那麼巧  我們就來到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  順便一提  雛菊小姐正在那邊陰影下休息著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  想不到我們會這麼好運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到我能在這麼美麗的地方與小颯二人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西澤同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不定運氣真的很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西…西澤同學  您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這點小事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼裡面好像進髒東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用手擦的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…小颯  能幫忙看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好像有條線一樣的東西在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  不是吧  能幫我拿掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  那請先別動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯…這是到哪裡去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  小颯明明都無法跟人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是到哪裡去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯  你一定要沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎怎怎怎怎怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就這樣  就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  拿下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人白擔心一場！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你都在幹些什麼啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯  你這傢伙真過分！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您…您誤會了  剛剛西澤同學的眼裡進了髒東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧小颯  現在已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,髒東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就放過你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑椿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它能把得到它的人的好運全部趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是招來不幸的  受詛咒的懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:27.73,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.38,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}渇いた心　持て余して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:33.19,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}展開なら気分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:36.05,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}刹那へと誘うあなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:40.61,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}戯れの中で　自由すぎるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:47.55,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:56.51,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}純真無垢な剣　振り翳す私を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:23:02.14,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}激しく射抜いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:02.38,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.43,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.99,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天使のような　微笑みで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:10.84,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}蜜よりも甘く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:16.37,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}恋の罠　仕掛けてみる（感じて）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:24.57,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“汝、今スグ　罪深キ　愛ノ概念ヲ　悔イ改メヨ”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:27.09,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}清らかに導かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:32.52,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}聖なる魂　あなたを抱きしめたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:27.73,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}Won't you show me all your secrets now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.38,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾澀的心蜷縮在荒漠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:33.19,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾澀了它的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.48,0:22:36.05,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剎那間被誘惑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:40.61,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在欺騙的愛中沉淪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:47.55,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)\an2}Get out……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:56.51,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望揮舞純真無邪之劍的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:23:02.14,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}盡情地讓疼痛貫穿我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:02.38,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an1}Just say you love me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.43,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}You know I've got a crush on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.99,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天使般的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:10.84,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}比蜜還甜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:16.37,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}設下愛情的陷阱（感受吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:24.57,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“汝那罪惡的愛情觀　現在立刻悔改吧”
